*ffmpeg-2.8.3-r1 (17 De 2015)

  17 Dec 2015; Matthias Hunstock <atze@fem.tu-ilmenau.de> +ffmpeg-2.8.3-r1.ebuild:
  version bump + cleanup

*ffmpeg-2.8-r2 (13 Oct 2015)

  13 Oct 2015; Peter Große <gentoo@friiks.de> -ffmpeg-2.1.1-r1.ebuild,
  -ffmpeg-2.4.3-r1.ebuild, -ffmpeg-2.5.4-r1.ebuild, ffmpeg-2.7.2-r1.ebuild,
  +ffmpeg-2.8-r2.ebuild, ffmpeg-9999.ebuild, metadata.xml:
  media-video/ffmpeg: patch current 2.8 release

  27 Aug 2015; Peter Große <gentoo@friiks.de> ffmpeg-2.6.3-r1.ebuild:
  mark as unstable

*ffmpeg-2.7.2-r1 (27 Aug 2015)
*ffmpeg-2.6.3-r1 (27 Aug 2015)

