  version bumps + cleanup

*ffmpeg-2.5.4-r1 (02 Mar 2015)

  02 Mar 2015; Peter Große <gentoo@friiks.de> +ffmpeg-2.5.4-r1.ebuild,
  ffmpeg-9999.ebuild:
  media-video/ffmpeg: add current ffmpeg version with decklink support

*ffmpeg-1.0 (27 Nov 2012)

  27 Nov 2012; Peter Grosse <gentoo@friiks.de> +ffmpeg-1.0.ebuild,
  +files/ffmpeg-1.0-segment-filename-timestamp.patch, +metadata.xml:
  add ffmpeg 1.0 with patch for segment format (support for timestamps as
  filenames)

